OL,5, Boots is changing the way its loyalty  
OL,6, card works by offering discounts on    
OL,7, more of its own-brand products but     
OL,8, cutting the points earned per pound.   
OL,10,FThe health and beauty retailer said    
OL,11,Fthat from May, holders of the Advantage
OL,12,FCard would collect 3p worth of points  
OL,13,Ffor every #1 spent, instead of 4p.     
OL,15,FThe move comes when many retailers'    
OL,16,Fcosts are increasing amidst record     
OL,17,Frises in energy bills and overheads.   
OL,19,FOne retail analyst said shoppers "want 
OL,20,Ftheir jam today rather than waiting".  
